  fhir:DomainResource.text [
     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "generated" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ConceptMap IMMZ.C.ConceptMap</b></p><a name=\"IMMZ.C.ConceptMap\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZ.C.ConceptMap\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Group 1 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.C.html\">IMMZ.C CodeSystem for Data Elements</a> to <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html\">AdministrativeGender</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>DE6 (Male)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>male</td></tr><tr><td>DE7 (Female)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>female</td></tr><tr><td>DE8 (Biological sex not specified)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>unknown</td></tr><tr><td>DE9 (Intersex)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#wider\" title=\"wider\">maps to wider concept</a></td><td>other</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 2 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-administrative-gender.html\">AdministrativeGender</a> to <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.C.html\">IMMZ.C CodeSystem for Data Elements</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td><td><b>Comment</b></td></tr><tr><td>male</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE6 (Male)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>female</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE7 (Female)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>unknown</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE8 (Biological sex not specified)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>other</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#narrower\" title=\"narrower\">narrower</a></td><td>DE9 (Intersex)</td><td>The DAK only provides Intersex as other options so the other from the source may be something else.</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 3 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.C.html\">IMMZ.C CodeSystem for Data Elements</a> to <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/6.1.0/CodeSystem-ICD11MMS.html\">International Classification of Diseases, 11th Revision Mortality and Morbidity Statistics (MMS)</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>DE6 (Male)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>XX2UQ8</td></tr><tr><td>DE7 (Female)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>XX2V25</td></tr><tr><td>DE8 (Biological sex not specified)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>XX2PX3</td></tr><tr><td>DE9 (Intersex)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>XX45B7</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 4 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/6.1.0/CodeSystem-ICD11MMS.html\">International Classification of Diseases, 11th Revision Mortality and Morbidity Statistics (MMS)</a> to <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.C.html\">IMMZ.C CodeSystem for Data Elements</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>XX2UQ8</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE6 (Male)</td></tr><tr><td>XX2V25</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE7 (Female)</td></tr><tr><td>XX2PX3</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE8 (Biological sex not specified)</td></tr><tr><td>XX45B7</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE9 (Intersex)</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 5 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.C.html\">IMMZ.C CodeSystem for Data Elements</a> to <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/6.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-loinc.html\">Logical Observation Identifiers, Names and Codes (LOINC)</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td><td><b>Comment</b></td></tr><tr><td>DE2 (Name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>54125-0 (Patient name)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>DE3 (First name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>45392-8 (Patient First (Given) name)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>DE4 (Family name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>45394-4 (Patient Last (Family) name)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>DE5 (Sex)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>46098-0 (Sex)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>DE10 (Date of birth)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>21112-8 (Birth date)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>DE13 (Age)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#wider\" title=\"wider\">maps to wider concept</a></td><td>63900-5 (Current age or age at death)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>DE16 (Caregiver's first name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#wider\" title=\"wider\">maps to wider concept</a></td><td>45392-8 (Patient First (Given) name)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>DE17 (Caregiver's family name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#wider\" title=\"wider\">maps to wider concept</a></td><td>45394-4 (Patient Last (Family) name)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>DE18 (Contact phone number)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>42077-8 (Patient phone number)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>DE19 (Address)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#narrower\" title=\"narrower\">narrower</a></td><td>56799-0 (Address)</td><td>Per the Immunizations DAK</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 6 </b>Mapping from <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/6.1.0/CodeSystem-v3-loinc.html\">Logical Observation Identifiers, Names and Codes (LOINC)</a> to <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZ.C.html\">IMMZ.C CodeSystem for Data Elements</a></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td><td><b>Comment</b></td></tr><tr><td>54125-0 (Patient name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE2 (Name)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>45392-8 (Patient First (Given) name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE3 (First name)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>45394-4 (Patient Last (Family) name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE4 (Family name)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>46098-0 (Sex)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE5 (Sex)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>21112-8 (Birth date)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE10 (Date of birth)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>63900-5 (Current age or age at death)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#narrower\" title=\"narrower\">narrower</a></td><td>DE13 (Age)</td><td>Per the Immunizations DAK</td></tr><tr><td>45392-8 (Patient First (Given) name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#narrower\" title=\"narrower\">narrower</a></td><td>DE16 (Caregiver's first name)</td><td>Per the Immunizations DAK</td></tr><tr><td>45394-4 (Patient Last (Family) name)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#narrower\" title=\"narrower\">narrower</a></td><td>DE17 (Caregiver's family name)</td><td>Per the Immunizations DAK</td></tr><tr><td>42077-8 (Patient phone number)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>DE18 (Contact phone number)</td><td/></tr><tr><td>56799-0 (Address)</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#wider\" title=\"wider\">maps to wider conce